text: Vusala Hajiyeva (born 3 October 1999) is an Azerbaijani footballer who plays as a midfielder for the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers Category:Russian Women's Football Championship players Category:Azerbaijani expatriate footballers Category:Azerbaijani expatriate sportspeople in Russia Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Russia
